IMPORT_LAST_FM_HISTORY_GUIDE:
1. Go to _LASTFM_CSV_LINK_

2. Type your username, fetch and download csv file.

3. Choose the file from the next screen.
IMPORT_YOUTUBE_HISTORY_GUIDE:
1. Go to _TAKEOUT_LINK_

2. Deselect All and select youtube only.

3. Press "Multiple Formats" and beside "History" choose "JSON".

4. Press "All Youtube data included", Deselect All and choose history only.

5. Create Export, Download & Unzip.

6. Choose "watch-history.json" from the next screen.
